OL,3,COwner of high street jewellers uses
OL,4,CVictorian baton to chase off armed
OL,5,Crobbers
OL,7,FThe owner of a high street jewellers
OL,8,Fused a Victorian baton to chase off
OL,9,Ftwo robbers armed with a chainsaw and
OL,10,Fmachete- but they still got away with
OL,11,F#75,000 worth of Rolex watches.
OL,13,FThe two men pulled up to Garnier
OL,14,FJewellers in Hoddesdon on a motorbike
OL,15,Fat around 11.15AM this Monday.
OL,17,FOne of the masked robbers used a power
OL,18,Ftool to cut into the glass.
OL,20,FWatch the moment the robbers broke
OL,21,Finto Garnier Jewellers:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
