OL,3,COwner of high street jewellers uses
OL,4,CVictorian baton to chase off armed
OL,5,Crobbers
OL,7,FInvestigating Officer, Detective
OL,8,FConstable John Ellams said:
OL,10,F"I would like to appeal to the public,
OL,11,Fwho may have crucial information which
OL,12,Fmay support our investigation into
OL,13,Fthis incident.
OL,15,F"At this time, our investigation is
OL,16,Fcontinuing and a lot of work is being
OL,17,Fcarried out by detectives, to try and
OL,18,Fidentify those responsible.
OL,26,@rD@AOUwD@AOU
